<div class="modal-content">
<div class="modal-header"><h5 class="modal-title"><i class="bi bi-shield-exclamation text-warning me-2"></i>FX Exposure &amp; Hedging</h5><button class="btn-close" (click)="closeModal()"></button></div>
<div class="modal-body">
<div class="row g-3 mb-3">
<div class="col-md-6"><div class="p-3 rounded" style="background:var(--pm-warning-soft)"><div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--pm-warning)">USD PAYABLES (30D)</div><div style="font-size:24px;font-weight:700;color:var(--pm-ink)">$ 42,500</div></div></div>
<div class="col-md-6"><div class="p-3 rounded" style="background:var(--pm-success-soft)"><div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--pm-accent)">USD RECEIVABLES (30D)</div><div style="font-size:24px;font-weight:700;color:var(--pm-ink)">$ 12,000</div></div></div>
</div>
<div class="p-3 rounded mb-3" style="background:var(--pm-surface-2);font-size:13px"><div class="d-flex justify-content-between mb-1"><span>Net Short Exposure</span><strong style="color:var(--pm-danger)">$ 30,500</strong></div><div class="d-flex justify-content-between mb-1"><span>Current Hedged Position</span><strong>$ 18,200 (Forward @ 130.10)</strong></div><div class="d-flex justify-content-between"><span>Unhedged Risk</span><strong style="color:var(--pm-warning)">$ 12,300</strong></div></div>
<h6 style="font-weight:700">Recommendation</h6>
<p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--pm-muted)">Consider booking a forward contract for the remaining $ 12,300 to lock in current rates before expected KES depreciation next month.</p>
</div>
